[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/negative_doubles"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST has a Limit Raise hand but after SOUTH's overcall a 3\H bid 
by WEST would be preemptive, not inviting. Instead he makes a Support Cue-bid.

EAST has just enough that she can bid 4\H, knowing that if WEST has 
a real block-buster he will bid on.

WEST doesn't have a real block-buster.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
